def AgeTen(df):
    g=sns.scatterplot(x="Age", y='Tenure', hue="Call_Flag", data=df)
    g.set(xscale='log')
    plt.show()
    plt.close()
In [8]:
def getCM(df):
    plt.figure(figsize=(16,16))
    sns.heatmap(df.corr(), annot=True)
    plt.show()
    plt.close()
In [9]:
def CP(df,y):
    print(df.groupby(y).size())
    sns.countplot(x=y, data=df,palette='hls')
    plt.title('Dataset Check - Imbalance')
    plt.show()
    plt.close()
